---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Investors | Fluidity Marine — $5M Seed Round">
  <main class="page">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="investor-hero animate-in">
      <div class="badge">
        <span class="badge-dot"></span>
        <span>Seed Round — $5M · Open on Wefunder</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="page-title">
        Join the <span class="electric-text">$5M Seed Raise</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">
        InnovativeDynamix is scaling the future of maritime technology. 
        Our ABLTV platform eliminates the mechanical rudder — an opportunity to participate 
        in a fundamental paradigm shift in marine propulsion. We are raising <strong>$5M</strong> 
        to bridge from prototype to production.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Quick Stats -->
    <section class="stats-grid animate-in delay-1">
      <div class="stat-card glass-box">
        <span class="stat-card-label">Raise Target</span>
        <span class="stat-card-value">$5,000,000</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card glass-box">
        <span class="stat-card-label">Platform</span>
        <span class="stat-card-value">Wefunder + SAFE</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card glass-box">
        <span class="stat-card-label">Technology</span>
        <span class="stat-card-value">ABLTV — 7-jet array</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card glass-box">
        <span class="stat-card-label">Cap (SAFE)</span>
        <span class="stat-card-value">$10M Valuation</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Investment Thesis -->
    <hr class="divider" />
    <section class="thesis-section animate-in delay-2">
      <h2 class="section-title">The Investment Thesis</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Why ABLTV represents a generational opportunity in marine technology.</p>

      <div class="thesis-grid">
        <div class="card thesis-card">
          <div class="thesis-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M16 8h-6a2 2 0 100 4h4a2 2 0 110 4H8"/><path d="M12 18V6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Massive TAM, Zero Competition</h3>
          <p>The global marine propulsion market is valued at $12B+ annually. No competitor offers a rudderless, software-defined thrust vectoring system. ABLTV is in a category of one.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card thesis-card">
          <div class="thesis-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Modular Moat</h3>
          <p>Our modular architecture enables regional manufacturing without centralized shipyards. Lower CapEx to scale, faster deployment, and supply chain resilience.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card thesis-card">
          <div class="thesis-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>IP-Protected Infrastructure</h3>
          <p><strong>5 patent families granted</strong> + 3 provisional filings covering ABLTV jet array, control algorithms, and boundary layer methodology. The system is entirely software-controlled, creating recurring revenue through over-the-air updates.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card thesis-card">
          <div class="thesis-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 010 8h-1"/><path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 01-4 4H6a4 4 0 01-4-4V8z"/><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"/><line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"/><line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Regulatory Tailwinds</h3>
          <p>Global emissions regulations are phasing out internal combustion marine engines. Electric propulsion is the only compliant path forward, and ABLTV is the most advanced electric propulsion architecture in development.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SAFE Term Summary -->
    <hr class="divider" />
    <section class="safe-section animate-in delay-2">
      <h2 class="section-title">SAFE Term Summary</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Simple, transparent terms for early backers.</p>

      <div class="glass-box">
        <div class="safe-grid">
          <div class="safe-item">
            <span class="safe-label">Instrument Type</span>
            <span class="safe-value">SAFE (Standard Y Combinator)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="safe-item">
            <span class="safe-label">Valuation Cap</span>
            <span class="safe-value highlight">$10,000,000</span>
          </div>
          <div class="safe-item">
            <span class="safe-label">Discount Rate</span>
            <span class="safe-value">20%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="safe-item">
            <span class="safe-label">MFN Clause</span>
            <span class="safe-value">Yes — automatic conversion to more favorable terms</span>
          </div>
          <div class="safe-item">
            <span class="safe-label">Minimum via Wefunder</span>
            <span class="safe-value">$500</span>
          </div>
          <div class="safe-item">
            <span class="safe-label">Private Placement Min</span>
            <span class="safe-value">$100,000 (accredited)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="safe-item">
            <span class="safe-label">Conversion Trigger</span>
            <span class="safe-value">Qualified financing ≥ $2M or change of control</span>
          </div>
          <div class="safe-item">
            <span class="safe-label">Investor Rights</span>
            <span class="safe-value">Information rights, pro-rata participation</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Use of Funds (Detailed) -->
    <hr class="divider" />
    <section class="funds-section animate-in delay-3">
      <h2 class="section-title">Use of Funds — $5M Seed Breakdown</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">How the seed capital will be deployed to scale ABLTV from prototype to global infrastructure.</p>

      <div class="funds-detailed">
        <div class="funds-block">
          <div class="funds-block-header">
            <div class="funds-bar" style="--bar-width: 30%; --bar-color: var(--cyan);"></div>
            <span class="funds-block-pct">30%</span>
            <span class="funds-block-amount">$1,500,000</span>
          </div>
          <h4>R&amp;D and Prototyping</h4>
          <p>Plugs, molds, composite fabrication for Fluidity One hull. Precision machining of 7-jet array components, pump procurement (high-pressure axial flow pumps, 200 L/s @ 30 m head), manifold assembly, and test stand. First three production hulls.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="funds-block">
          <div class="funds-block-header">
            <div class="funds-bar" style="--bar-width: 24%; --bar-color: #00e5a0;"></div>
            <span class="funds-block-pct">24%</span>
            <span class="fuels-block-amount">$1,200,000</span>
          </div>
          <h4>Propulsion System Integration</h4>
          <p>Precision machining of all jet array components, pump procurement, manifold assembly, and full test stand. Instrumentation (pressure sensors, flow meters, IMUs) and three trial cycles (bench → dock → underway).</p>
        </div>

        <div class="funds-block">
          <div class="funds-block-header">
            <div class="funds-bar" style="--bar-width: 16%; --bar-color: #7c6df0;"></div>
            <span class="funds-block-pct">16%</span>
            <span class="funds-block-amount">$800,000</span>
          </div>
          <h4>On-Water Trials</h4>
          <p>Instrumentation, test crew salaries, three trial cycles: bench → dock → underway. Comprehensive sea trial program including performance validation, endurance testing, and regulatory certification support.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="funds-block">
          <div class="funds-block-header">
            <div class="funds-bar" style="--bar-width: 14%; --bar-color: #f0a36d;"></div>
            <span class="funds-block-pct">14%</span>
            <span class="funds-block-amount">$700,000</span>
          </div>
          <h4>Team Expansion</h4>
          <p>4 key hires: Senior CFD Engineer (fluid-structure interaction), Mechatronics Engineer (actuator integration), Embedded SW Engineer (control firmware, OTA pipeline), Marine Test Pilot (on-water operations).</p>
        </div>

        <div class="funds-block">
          <div class="funds-block-header">
            <div class="funds-bar" style="--bar-width: 8%; --bar-color: #f06d8a;"></div>
            <span class="funds-block-pct">8%</span>
            <span class="funds-block-amount">$400,000</span>
          </div>
          <h4>IP &amp; Regulatory</h4>
          <p>Patent prosecution (3 utility + 2 design patents), USCG / ABYC certification for electric propulsion systems, insurance, legal counsel.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="funds-block">
          <div class="funds-block-header">
            <div class="funds-bar" style="--bar-width: 8%; --bar-color: #4facfe;"></div>
            <span class="funds-block-pct">8%</span>
            <span class="funds-block-amount">$400,000</span>
          </div>
          <h4>Operations</h4>
          <p>Facility lease (waterfront test site), legal, accounting, G&A, working capital buffer.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Financial Projections -->
    <hr class="divider" />
    <section class="financials-section animate-in delay-3">
      <h2 class="section-title">3-Year Projections</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Capital-efficient path to a licensing-driven, high-margin business model.</p>

      <div class="comparison-table-wrapper">
        <table class="financials-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>USD (000s)</th>
              <th>Year 1 (2027)</th>
              <th>Year 2 (2028)</th>
              <th>Year 3 (2029)</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Revenue</strong></td>
              <td class="cyan-cell">$250</td>
              <td class="cyan-cell">$1,200</td>
              <td class="cyan-cell">$4,800</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Direct Sales</td>
              <td>$250 (2 vessels)</td>
              <td>$750 (5 vessels)</td>
              <td>$1,200 (8 vessels)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>OEM Licensing</td>
              <td>$0</td>
              <td>$300 (1 co-dev)</td>
              <td>$2,400 (3 OEMs)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Aftermarket</td>
              <td>$0</td>
              <td>$150</td>
              <td>$1,200</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Gross Profit</strong></td>
              <td>$87 (35%)</td>
              <td>$480 (40%)</td>
              <td class="cyan-cell">$2,160 (45%)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>R&amp;D</td>
              <td>($600)</td>
              <td>($400)</td>
              <td>($400)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>SG&amp;A</td>
              <td>($400)</td>
              <td>($500)</td>
              <td>($600)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Net Income</strong></td>
              <td class="amber-cell">($913)</td>
              <td class="amber-cell">($420)</td>
              <td class="cyan-cell"><strong>$1,160</strong></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="financials-note">Breakeven target: Q3 2029. Cumulative capital needed to breakeven: ~$6.2M ($5M seed + $1.2M bridge or non-dilutive grant). Grant runway (SBIR, DOE, NSF) actively pursued.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Team Section -->
    <hr class="divider" />
    <section class="team-section animate-in delay-3">
      <h2 class="section-title">The Team</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Deep theory meets hands-on execution. Founders who can derive the physics, build the hardware, and write the control code.</p>

      <div class="team-grid">
        <div class="card team-card team-lead">
          <div class="team-avatar">AE</div>
          <div class="team-info">
            <h3>Aaron Evans</h3>
            <span class="team-role">CEO / Chief Scientist</span>
            <p>Inventor of ABLTV. Conceived the thrust vectoring architecture, validated first-principles fluid dynamics through CFD across 200+ hull configurations, and led bench-scale prototype to 87% thrust efficiency. Cross-disciplinary: naval architecture, mechatronics, and embedded control. Can both derive the Navier-Stokes simplification and weld the test stand.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card team-card">
          <div class="team-avatar">NT</div>
          <div class="team-info">
            <h3>Natasha</h3>
            <span class="team-role">CTO — Control Architect</span>
            <p>Controls engineering and embedded systems lead. Responsible for the real-time multi-variable PID + ML control layer that modulates the 7-jet array at millisecond granularity. Architect of the firmware that competitors cannot replicate.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 class="team-hiring-title">Key Hires (Post-Seed)</h3>
      <div class="hiring-grid">
        <div class="glass-box hiring-card">
          <div class="hiring-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4"/><path d="M12 8h.01"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Senior CFD Engineer</h4>
          <p>Fluid-structure interaction modeling, jet-hull coupling optimization, cavitation prediction</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-box hiring-card">
          <div class="hiring-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"/><rect x="2" y="14" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="6.01" y2="6"/><line x1="6" y1="18" x2="6.01" y2="18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Mechatronics Engineer</h4>
          <p>Actuator integration, high-pressure pump control, manifold sensor fusion</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-box hiring-card">
          <div class="hiring-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Embedded SW Engineer</h4>
          <p>Real-time control firmware, sensor drivers, OTA update pipeline</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-box hiring-card">
          <div class="hiring-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Marine Test Pilot</h4>
          <p>On-water test execution, instrumentation, safety protocols</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Data Room -->
    <hr class="divider" />
    <section class="datacenter-section animate-in delay-3">
      <h2 class="section-title">Data Room</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Comprehensive due diligence materials for qualified investors.</p>

      <div class="data-room-grid">
        <a href="/DATA_ROOM_TEMPLATES/executive-summary.pdf" class="card data-room-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <div class="data-room-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Executive Summary</h4>
          <p>Company overview, technology, market, and investment highlights</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/DATA_ROOM_TEMPLATES/pitch-deck.pdf" class="card data-room-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <div class="data-room-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/><line x1="9" y1="21" x2="9" y2="9"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Pitch Deck</h4>
          <p>Full investor deck covering all aspects of the opportunity</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/DATA_ROOM_TEMPLATES/financial-model.xlsx" class="card data-room-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <div class="data-room-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="8" y1="16" x2="16" y2="16"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/><line x1="8" y1="20" x2="12" y2="20"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Financial Model</h4>
          <p>Detailed 5-year projections, unit economics, and sensitivity analysis</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/DATA_ROOM_TEMPLATES/tech-brief.pdf" class="card data-room-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <div class="data-room-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Technical Brief</h4>
          <p>Complete ABLTV engineering specifications and performance data</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Vision Brief -->
    <hr class="divider" />
    <section class="vision-section animate-in delay-3">
      <h2 class="section-title">Scaling the Maritime Operating System</h2>
      <p class="vision-text">
        Fluidity Marine is more than a propulsion company. We are building the modular IP core — 
        ABLTV — that will power a new generation of high-efficiency, low-maintenance vessels. 
        From commercial transit to aspirational lifestyle anchors like <strong>The Floating Bar</strong>, 
        our technology is the common denominator.
      </p>

      <div class="vision-stats">
        <div class="vision-stat">
          <span class="vision-stat-value">$12B+</span>
          <span class="vision-stat-label">Total Addressable Market</span>
        </div>
        <div class="vision-stat">
          <span class="vision-stat-value">60%</span>
          <span class="vision-stat-label">Fewer Failure Points</span>
        </div>
        <div class="vision-stat">
          <span class="vision-stat-value">100%</span>
          <span class="vision-stat-label">Electric Propulsion</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Milestones -->
    <hr class="divider" />
    <section class="milestones-section animate-in delay-3">
      <h2 class="section-title">Roadmap & Milestones</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Our path from laboratory to global infrastructure.</p>

      <div class="milestone-timeline">
        <div class="milestone completed">
          <div class="milestone-marker"></div>
          <div class="milestone-content">
            <span class="milestone-status">Completed</span>
            <h3>ABLTV Proof of Concept</h3>
            <p>Validated Active Boundary Layer Thrust Vectoring through fluid dynamic simulation and rapid prototyping. 87% propulsive efficiency achieved at bench scale.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="milestone active">
          <div class="milestone-marker"></div>
          <div class="milestone-content">
            <span class="milestone-status">Active</span>
            <h3>Seed Round &amp; Web Presence</h3>
            <p>$5M seed round open on Wefunder. Building the digital and physical infrastructure for scaled production. 5 patent families granted.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="milestone">
          <div class="milestone-marker"></div>
          <div class="milestone-content">
            <span class="milestone-status">Q3 2026</span>
            <h3>Technical Whitepaper Release</h3>
            <p>Comprehensive publication of ABLTV engineering specifications, simulation results, and performance data for qualified investors and partners.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="milestone">
          <div class="milestone-marker"></div>
          <div class="milestone-content">
            <span class="milestone-status">Q1 2027</span>
            <h3>First Full-Array On-Water Test</h3>
            <p>First full 7-jet ABLTV system on water — Fluidity One hull, integrated pump, manifold, and full controller stack.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="milestone">
          <div class="milestone-marker"></div>
          <div class="milestone-content">
            <span class="milestone-status">Q3 2027</span>
            <h3>Commercial Pilot Program</h3>
            <p>3 pilot vessels deployed with beachhead partners: charter fleet (Florida Keys), marine research org, high-end dealer. 4–6 month telemetry collection and NPS scoring.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="milestone">
          <div class="milestone-marker"></div>
          <div class="milestone-content">
            <span class="milestone-status">2028</span>
            <h3>First OEM Co-Development</h3>
            <p>First OEM integration contract signed. ABLTV becomes a production option on a production boat. Licensing model begins validation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Investor FAQ -->
    <hr class="divider" />
    <section class="faq-section animate-in delay-3">
      <h2 class="section-title">Investor FAQ</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Answers to the most common questions from prospective investors.</p>

      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item glass-box">
          <h4>What is the minimum investment?</h4>
          <p>$500 via Wefunder (community round). $100,000 minimum for private placement accredited investors. $50,000 minimum for private SAFE.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item glass-box">
          <h4>What is the valuation and instrument type?</h4>
          <p>Wefunder community round uses a SAFE with a $10M valuation cap and 20% discount. Private placement offers Series Seed Preferred Stock with standard information rights, pro-rata participation, and voting rights.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item glass-box">
          <h4>How will the funds be used?</h4>
          <p>30% R&amp;D and prototyping (Fluidity One hull, tooling), 24% propulsion system integration, 16% on-water trials, 14% team expansion (4 hires), 8% IP and regulatory, 8% operations and working capital.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item glass-box">
          <h4>What is the revenue model?</h4>
          <p>Three-channel approach: Direct sales (limited Fluidity One vessels at $180K–$250K), OEM licensing (8–12% royalty on MSRP), and aftermarket services (firmware subscriptions at $500/yr, performance analytics, refurbished jet exchanges).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item glass-box">
          <h4>What is the competitive advantage?</h4>
          <p>ABLTV is the only rudderless, software-defined thrust vectoring system. No competitor offers zero-appendage drag, 7-jet redundancy, full OTA-updateable controls, or 87% propulsive efficiency. Protected by 5 granted patent families.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item glass-box">
          <h4>What is the path to profitability?</h4>
